Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:07.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}その頂きへと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}We must be the change we wish to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:15.28,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}在囚籠中是絕對安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:20.47,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}但忘卻了創造的地方不會有光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.95,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}訴說希望 驅散不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.85,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}革命的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:29.41,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}突破到無人能及的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:35.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}總有一天要超越修羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:40.95,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}就算現在壓倒性的支配讓我極度乾渴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:45.45,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}只有夢不會被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:48.37,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}燃燒吧 全部神經的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:53.14,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不知誰能收到的聲音裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:58.47,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不會有意義
